name:                uzbl-with-source
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            Utility function for reading a source of loaded uzbl pages.
description:         Utility function for reading a source of loaded uzbl
                     pages. It attemps to read the UZBL_SOCKET variable passed in
                     by uzbl during runtime and extract source by probing it.
                     The program ‘socat’ is a run-time dependency.
